These samples use Angular 2.0 rc-5

Live DEMO here: http://www.syntaxsuccess.com/angular-2-samples
Documentation: http://www.syntaxsuccess.com/angular-2-articles

Here are the prerequisites for running the project:

1-npm install -g typescript

2-npm install

3-bower install

4-npm run run bundle (create a single bundle file using rollup with tree shaking)

5-npm run es5 (convert bundle to es5)

6-npm run minify (minfy and mangle bundle)

Steps 1-3 will install the required tooling.

Step 4-6 creates a javascript bundle that will be loaded when the site launches

The final step is to launch the site by starting the lite-server

npm run start

